1. *Bombe* su učestale u ovom gradu. (Bombs are frequent in this city.)
2. Njegov otac je bio u *bombi*. (His father was in the bomb.)
3. On je napravio *bombu*. (He made the bomb.)
4. *Bombama* su izazvani veliki štetni efekti. (Big damage effects were caused by bombs.)
5. Oni su razbili *bombu*. (They smashed the bomb.)
6. *Bombu* su postavili u blizini škole. (They placed the bomb near the school.)
7. On je napravio *bombe*. (He made bombs.)
8. *Bombe* su eksplodirale. (The bombs exploded.)